As you may be aware, we are in toolchain freeze and the release team
has asked toolchain package maintainers[1] to stop uploading these
packages, which includes gcc. So unless the bug
report is very critical, the fix for the said bug _might not_ be
uploaded.

And so it may be a good idea to go ahead with the workaround.

[1]: https://lists.debian.org/debian-devel-announce/2023/01/msg00004.html

